    {
      "id": "4c7f7f9b",
      "type": "table",
      "isFinalized": true,
      "payload": {
        "raw": "| Category | Streamdown | StreamMDX |\n| --- | --- | --- |\n| Execution model | Main-thread React rendering | Worker-first parse pipeline with incremental patch application |\n| Rendering surface | React component, close to `react-markdown` ergonomics | Dedicated `StreamingMarkdown` renderer plus lower-level packages |\n| Incremental model | Incomplete-markdown resilience + memoized rerendering | Explicit semantic/enrichment patch batches committed to a stable render tree |\n| Long-document posture | Main-thread work scales with content updates | Worker offload, queueing, and patch scheduling intended to reduce main-thread pressure |\n| Packaging | Single package | Modular packages plus `stream-mdx` convenience wrapper |",
